    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName key="#Bishops #Popes" ref="#people/2140">Leo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Popes">servus servorum Dei</rs>
                        <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/2143">Wiberto</persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/38">Mutinensi</placeName> episcopo, salutem et
                        apostolicam benedictionem. Mirabilis Deus in sanctis suis, gloriosus et
                        mitis, et magnae misericordiae et super maliciam prestabilis, multorum
                        fidelium ut vera conperimus relacione, centupla remuneratione donavit,
                        sancti sui confessoris meritum et laborem <persName
                            key="#Monks #Deacons #Churches"><name ref="Symeon"
                            >Symeonis</name></persName>. Reverentissimo <rs key="#Abbots"
                            >abbati</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancto
                            Benedicto</orgName> exhibeatur honor, adiuncto sibi sotio Symeone <rs
                            key="#Monks">monacho</rs>, heremita et <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs>.
                            <placeName ref="#places/275">Mantuanus</placeName> episcopus novam ibi
                        consecrabit <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs>, cui volumus ut exhibeas
                        honorificentiam, scilicet interesse te volumus huic consecrationi, et huius
                        corporis elevationi, et altare in eius honore consecretur, quem Deus summa
                        virtutum clarificavit dignitate.</ab>
                </div>
